title: El-Sissi Is Clear Front-Runner In Egypt Presidential Contest
teaser: Egyptians go to the polls this week, and the front-runner is Abdel-Fattah el-Sisi. His supporters say he'll bring order to the country, but others say Mohammed Morsi is still the legitimate president.
